---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Ori Simantov — Founder of AgentsOrg"
  description="Ori Simantov is an AI transformation leader and data scientist with 10+ years of experience scaling enterprise AI. He built AgentsOrg to solve the governance gap he encountered leading large-scale AI adoption programs."
>
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Hero -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start gap-10 mb-16">
        <img
          src="/ori-simantov.jpg"
          alt="Ori Simantov"
          class="w-32 h-32 rounded-2xl object-cover shrink-0 border border-border"
        />
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-2">Ori Simantov</h1>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-4">AI Transformation Leader &middot; Builder &middot; Open Source</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ori-simantov-5545a9119/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface text-sm text-text-muted hover:border-accent/50 hover:text-text transition-all"
            >
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#0A66C2]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
              LinkedIn
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/ori129/agentsorg"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface text-sm text-text-muted hover:border-accent/50 hover:text-text transition-all"
            >
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
              GitHub
            </a>
            <a
              href="mailto:ori129@gmail.com"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-surface text-sm text-text-muted hover:border-accent/50 hover:text-text transition-all"
            >
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
              Email
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Why AgentsOrg -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5">Why I Built AgentsOrg</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I've spent over a decade building data science and AI systems inside enterprise organizations — turning complex datasets into operational intelligence and embedding AI into everyday workflows.
          </p>
          <p>
            When leading large-scale AI adoption programs, I kept running into the same problem: as AI creation spread across teams, visibility collapsed. No one knew what had been built, who built it, whether it was any good, or whether three different teams had built the same thing. The governance gap was real and no tooling existed to close it.
          </p>
          <p>
            I built the internal tooling to solve it. AgentsOrg is that — open sourced so every AI transformation leader can benefit from it, not just one organization.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- OpenAI recognition -->
      <div class="mb-12 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-accent/20 bg-surface">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Recognized by OpenAI</p>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
              The enterprise AI transformation program Ori led was featured by OpenAI as an example of organizations successfully embedding AI into internal workflows at scale.
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://openai.com/index/hibob/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mt-3 text-accent text-sm font-medium hover:underline"
            >
              Read the OpenAI case study
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Background -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5">Background</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          {[
            { label: '10+ years', desc: 'Building data science and AI systems across enterprise organizations — from analytical models and data pipelines to AI agents and workflow automation.' },
            { label: 'Enterprise AI adoption', desc: 'Designing internal governance frameworks, enabling employees to build AI tools, and creating adoption programs that scale AI usage across entire organizations.' },
            { label: 'AI agents & workflow intelligence', desc: 'Building AI systems that automate operational tasks, surface insights from complex datasets, and embed intelligence directly into everyday work across platforms like Salesforce, Snowflake, and others.' },
            { label: 'AI Mind', desc: 'Founder of the AI Mind initiative — a program focused on scaling AI literacy, governance, and operational capability across large organizations.' },
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="flex gap-4 p-5 rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface">
              <div class="text-accent font-semibold text-sm shrink-0 w-32">{item.label}</div>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission -->
      <div class="mb-12 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border bg-surface">
        <blockquote class="text-lg text-text leading-relaxed font-medium">
          "AI transformation is not about tools. It's about building systems that combine data, models, and workflows to create measurable business impact — and making sure those systems are governed, discoverable, and improving over time."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a
          href="/advisors"
          class="flex-1 py-3.5 rounded-xl bg-accent text-white font-semibold hover:bg-accent/90 transition-all text-center text-sm"
        >
          Join the Advisor Directory
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/ori129/agentsorg"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="flex-1 py-3.5 rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface text-text font-semibold hover:border-accent/50 transition-all text-center text-sm"
        >
          View AgentsOrg on GitHub
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:ori129@gmail.com"
          class="flex-1 py-3.5 rounded-xl border border-border bg-surface text-text font-semibold hover:border-accent/50 transition-all text-center text-sm"
        >
          Get in Touch
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
